  m_text: 'Day 43

    Their voices can no longer be heard. The crying has stopped.All
    preparations for the ritual are finally complete.

    Only one more sacrifice
    is needed.It is getting closer.I can feel its presence.It is down below.It is
    calling to me.

    Soon, everything will begin.'
